elevation.label: Elevation
elevation.description: The elevation of a location (WGS 84). Values may be of the form 'NUMBER UNIT_OF_MEASUREMENT' (e.g., '1,000 m', '3,200 ft') while numbers alone should be assumed to be a value in meters.

area.label: Area
area.description: The area of a Spatial Object in square meters

within.label: Within
within.description: States that the subject SpatialObject is spatially within the object SpatialObject. DE-9IM: T*F**F***

finishedBy.label: Finished By
finishedBy.description: If a proper interval T1 is intervalFinishedBy another proper interval T2, then the beginning of T1 is before the beginning of T2, and the end of T1 is coincident with the end of T2.
